[Student "S"]
{The bidding has been as shown.  

If you had been the dealer you would have opened 2\S. The situation is no different after they open so you Overcall 2\S. Everybody passes.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "3"]
[Dealer "S"]
[Vulnerable "EW"]
[Deal "S:QT.542.KQ742.A94 975.KQJ97.83.K52 42.AT86.AJT9.J83 AKJ863.3.65.QT76"]
[Declarer "E"]
